install TS:
*Globally 
npm install -g typescript 
=============================================
*Locally
npm install typescript __save-dev
=============================================
check version
-> tsc --version or tsc -v
===============================================
save the file  javascript -> .js


save the file typescript -> .ts

convert your ts code to js code
cmd -> tsc filename.ts (file convert as .js)


it covert into js code


cmd -> node filename.js(output)